{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":2000,"text":"(Singing)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":17823,"text":"(Singing ends)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":122911,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":131519,"text":"Pep Rosenfeld: Folks,\nyou've just met Claron McFadden."},{"time":134551,"text":"She is a world-class soprano singer"},{"time":137162,"text":"who studied in Rochester, New York."},{"time":139678,"text":"Her celebrated operatic roles\nare numerous and varied."},{"time":143389,"text":"In August 2007, Claron was awarded\nthe Amsterdam Prize for the Arts,"},{"time":148984,"text":"winning praise for her brilliance,"},{"time":150823,"text":"her amazing and extensively\nwide repertoire"},{"time":154253,"text":"and her vivid stage personality."},{"time":156444,"text":"Please welcome Claron McFadden."}]},{"cues":[{"time":158414,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":169400,"text":"Claron McFadden: The human voice:"},{"time":172074,"text":"mysterious, spontaneous, primal."},{"time":177793,"text":"For me, the human voice is the vessel\non which all emotions travel --"},{"time":182754,"text":"except, perhaps, jealousy."},{"time":186580,"text":"And the breath,"},{"time":188079,"text":"the breath is the captain of that vessel."},{"time":192331,"text":"A child is born,"},{"time":195298,"text":"takes its first breath --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":197603,"text":"(Inhales)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":202750,"text":"Whah!"},{"time":205271,"text":"And we behold the wondrous beauty"},{"time":209694,"text":"of vocal expression --"},{"time":211928,"text":"mysterious, spontaneous"},{"time":215639,"text":"and primal."}]},{"cues":[{"time":218663,"text":"A few years ago, I did\na meditation retreat in Thailand."},{"time":221829,"text":"I wanted a place"},{"time":224019,"text":"where I would have total silence\nand total solitude."},{"time":228728,"text":"I spent two weeks at this retreat"},{"time":231359,"text":"in my own little hut --"},{"time":233097,"text":"no music, no nothing -- sounds of nature,"},{"time":236954,"text":"trying to find the essence\nof concentration,"},{"time":240517,"text":"being in the moment."}]},{"cues":[{"time":242677,"text":"On my last day,"},{"time":244558,"text":"the woman who looked after the place,"},{"time":247415,"text":"she came and we spoke for a minute,"},{"time":249615,"text":"and then she said to me,"},{"time":252321,"text":"\"Would you sing something for me?\""},{"time":254655,"text":"And I thought, but this is a place\nof total quiet and silence."},{"time":257956,"text":"I can't make noise."},{"time":260550,"text":"She said, \"Please, sing for me.\""},{"time":264293,"text":"So I closed my eyes,"},{"time":266920,"text":"I took breath"},{"time":269840,"text":"and the first thing that came up and out"},{"time":273205,"text":"was \"Summertime,\""},{"time":275777,"text":"Porgy and Bess."}]},{"cues":[{"time":276999,"text":"(Singing) Summertime\nand the livin' is easy."},{"time":282372,"text":"Fish are jumpin' and the cotton is high."},{"time":285538,"text":"Oh, your daddy's rich\nand your ma is good-lookin'."},{"time":289547,"text":"So hush little baby,"},{"time":291161,"text":"don't you cry."}]},{"cues":[{"time":294843,"text":"And I opened my eyes,"},{"time":297213,"text":"and I saw that she had her eyes closed."},{"time":300741,"text":"And after a moment, she opened her eyes"},{"time":302868,"text":"and she looked at me and she said,"},{"time":305765,"text":"\"It's like meditation.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":308505,"text":"And in that moment I understood"},{"time":310751,"text":"that everything I had gone\nto Thailand to look for,"},{"time":314187,"text":"to search for,"},{"time":315797,"text":"I had it already in my singing --"},{"time":319606,"text":"the calm, but alertness,"},{"time":323400,"text":"the focus, but awareness,"},{"time":326544,"text":"and being totally in the moment."},{"time":331035,"text":"When you're totally in the moment --"},{"time":332805,"text":"when I'm totally in the moment,"},{"time":334328,"text":"the vessel of expression is open."},{"time":336557,"text":"The emotions can flow from me"},{"time":339153,"text":"to you"},{"time":340350,"text":"and back."},{"time":342557,"text":"It's an extremely profound experience."}]},{"cues":[{"time":346787,"text":"There's a piece by a composer,"},{"time":349161,"text":"an American composer called John Cage."},{"time":351783,"text":"It's called \"Aria.\""},{"time":353387,"text":"It was written for an amazing singer\ncalled Cathy Berberian."},{"time":358492,"text":"And the thing about this piece\nthat's so special --"},{"time":361682,"text":"if you see it behind me --"},{"time":364007,"text":"it's not notated in any way."},{"time":367409,"text":"No notes, no flats, no sharps."},{"time":370798,"text":"But it's a kind of structure."},{"time":373171,"text":"And the singer, within this structure,"},{"time":375655,"text":"has total freedom\nto be creative, spontaneous."}]},{"cues":[{"time":380278,"text":"For example,"},{"time":382572,"text":"there are different colors"},{"time":384143,"text":"and each color gets\na different type of singing --"},{"time":388119,"text":"pop, country and western, opera, jazz --"},{"time":392032,"text":"and you just have\nto be consistent with that color."},{"time":396350,"text":"You see there are different lines."},{"time":398738,"text":"You choose in your own tempo\nin your own way"},{"time":400969,"text":"to follow the line,"},{"time":402246,"text":"but you must respect it,"},{"time":404466,"text":"more or less."},{"time":406131,"text":"And these little dots,"},{"time":408646,"text":"these represent a sort of sound"},{"time":413199,"text":"that's not a vocal, not a lyrical way"},{"time":416000,"text":"of expressing the voice."},{"time":418231,"text":"Using the body -- it could be sneezing,"},{"time":420316,"text":"it could be coughing, animals --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":421919,"text":"(Audience member coughs)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":423538,"text":"Exactly. (Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":424854,"text":"Clapping, whatever."},{"time":427878,"text":"And there's different text."},{"time":429869,"text":"There's Armenian, Russian,\nFrench, English, Italian."},{"time":434199,"text":"So within this structure, one is free."},{"time":437685,"text":"To me, this piece is an ode to the voice,"},{"time":441732,"text":"because it's mysterious, as we can see."},{"time":446153,"text":"It's quite spontaneous."},{"time":450551,"text":"And it's primal."},{"time":452505,"text":"So I would like to share\nthis piece with you,"},{"time":454719,"text":"It's \"Aria,\" of John Cage."}]},{"cues":[{"time":464268,"text":"(Singing in various languages)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":465745,"text":"Hampart-zoum"}]},{"cues":[{"time":471444,"text":"Dirouhi"}]},{"cues":[{"time":472964,"text":"Di questa Terra"}]},{"cues":[{"time":475345,"text":"Naprasno"}]},{"cues":[{"time":478773,"text":"Conscience et"}]},{"cues":[{"time":480940,"text":"(Barks)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":483321,"text":"(Singing) Arise"}]},{"cues":[{"time":490731,"text":"Tsk, tsk, tsk."}]},{"cues":[{"time":493501,"text":"(Singing)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":494659,"text":"Vidiel’a"}]},{"cues":[{"time":496617,"text":"facilmente"}]},{"cues":[{"time":499109,"text":"E io sono per te"}]},{"cues":[{"time":503863,"text":"(Robotic voice) No other way"}]},{"cues":[{"time":505458,"text":"Dans l'espace, so help"}]},{"cues":[{"time":508787,"text":"(Singing)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":509946,"text":"Si juste"}]},{"cues":[{"time":513112,"text":"Dvidzénya bistri"}]},{"cues":[{"time":519891,"text":"(Claps)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":521923,"text":"(Singing)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":523081,"text":"On pekrásen"}]},{"cues":[{"time":524764,"text":"idyot a k u"}]},{"cues":[{"time":529526,"text":"O a k ho a"}]},{"cues":[{"time":534977,"text":"Sivayoot eternal loosin"}]},{"cues":[{"time":541477,"text":"(Sneezes)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":546540,"text":"(Laughs)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":547842,"text":"Shh!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":552501,"text":"(Singing)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":553651,"text":"Gloobinoí più chiara"}]},{"cues":[{"time":558254,"text":"Si ceci est cela cela est ceci"}]},{"cues":[{"time":566973,"text":"Totalmente soi whom they sought to slay"}]},{"cues":[{"time":573451,"text":"To have the fruits gloire"}]},{"cues":[{"time":577915,"text":"J’écoute ..."}]},{"cues":[{"time":580479,"text":"À la vie…"}]},{"cues":[{"time":583003,"text":"Leggermente snédznoi"}]},{"cues":[{"time":590113,"text":"Coo coo"}]},{"cues":[{"time":592033,"text":"P k t d"}]},{"cues":[{"time":595478,"text":"Banalité"}]},{"cues":[{"time":597986,"text":"K o e"}]},{"cues":[{"time":602083,"text":"(Makes the sound of a kiss)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":605734,"text":"(Singing)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":606909,"text":"In armonia"}]},{"cues":[{"time":617269,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}